<plot>This is a film noir short about John, a lieutenant in a crime organization. He is married to Eva and they have a daughter, Jennifer. John botches a major drug deal and now he has to pay the price. Two killers are on their way to bring him for a "final meeting". John wants to go quietly to protect his family but they want to fight. How does he get out of this mess?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?461106</url></doc>
